    "Name": "\"Bloodlust\"",
    "Details": "The Vulcan VT-BL, better known as the \"Bloodlust\", is a special variant of the Vulcan that focuses on its strengths as an anti-infantry 'Mech. Its weaponry consists of two Machine Guns in the left arm, with a Small Laser and another Machine Gun in the right arm. The head, right and left torsos each carry a SRM-4, while four tons of ammo help keep them sufficiently supplied. Powered by a 240 XL engine to mount such a heavy weapons loadout, the Bloodlust retains the same armor volume and single heat sinks of the common VL-2T variant.",
